@startuml US07_Signup_With_Email_OTP
title US-07: Email Signup with OTP Verification (Guest User)

|Guest User|
start
:(1) Open signup form;
:(2) Enter email and submit;

|System|
:(3) Send OTP to provided email;

|Guest User|
:(4) Enter OTP code;

|System|
:(5) Validate OTP;
if (OTP valid?) then (Yes)
  |Guest User|
  :(6) Set username and password;
  |System|
  :(7) Create account and start session;
  |Guest User|
  :(8) See signup success and continue;
else (No)
  |Guest User|
  :(6) Re-enter OTP or request new code;
endif

stop
@enduml
